Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.20,0:02:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德克撒斯攻防战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.61,0:02:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二战斗范围，没有异样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.11,0:02:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有敌舰，没有敌军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.72,0:02:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.29,0:02:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有30分钟就交替呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去检查他的血压吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保史加，马加，阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好好的维持呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳‧波也要负责做不同的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很辛苦呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和阿姆罗来比，舒服很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何时开始的？         什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们没有说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.45,0:03:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢！因在拚命呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从电脑的诊察，没异常地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗变得可怕的强壮呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像追不上呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是好了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因不想看到懦弱的阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也变成大人起来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.28,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！芙劳‧波，我什么也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.82,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在卫星六号发生了什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗好像改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如终有一天能说出来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会和你说呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇到不同的事      是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？         没有异常地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人的情况怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很顺利，是因为有在运动吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，德克撒斯有不明朗的颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要避开吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.52,0:04:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弄醒你，对不起！         不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第三战斗范围是知比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在德克撒斯也好像有呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.29,0:04:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃出了所罗门的白色基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.43,0:04:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入了德克撒斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.00,0:04:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有不明朗的颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.27,0:04:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用利亚和专门科技制造的这卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.27,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被叫做德克撒斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.01,0:04:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了军事的重要，而被留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了要隐藏，留下了岩石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.61,0:05:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和卫星的残骸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还未到达德克撒斯吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贝路米士和比多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像因整备而迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，只要我的盖古克到达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在德克撒斯有人在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...以前的从业员和卫星的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理人是仅有一点在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是像个无人的卫星吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.47,0:05:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,附近马克贝在的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边没有多余武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由他们去做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙自巴鲁进入德克撒斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知比移动了，好像被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.39,0:05:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！全体人员行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人接近！敌人接近！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体人员战斗开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.13,0:05:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗后的好好洗澡竟然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想是所罗门逃走的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如进入了第二战斗范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.68,0:06:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢加农也要出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，不要大意所罗门的余党
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱，可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令你担心，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想做点工作去除疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.42,0:06:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要勉强来，如我可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可和你倾诉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.39,0:06:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样的话，帮了我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和预定一样，可以捉着木马吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乌拿加，我的甘恩整备怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何时也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！在进到去第二区域出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用甘恩出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.19,0:06:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，不用马克贝上校亲自出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.09,0:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甘恩是我开发的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是作为基西利亚男人的面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.04,0:07:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有夏亚的那MS有否送到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.27,0:07:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他面前看我收拾木马和钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.81,0:07:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，知比能捕捉第二区域的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请小心一点         知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地点3A，捕捉到木马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各人进入战斗配置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆，在等待敌人战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备战斗状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如钢弹出现后，去引诱它吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样甘恩会容易去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.93,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了！         那样去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了吧！雪拉，是知比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多可看到了      明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马加，敌方的移动怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩石不断的增多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正面，最大防卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在瞄着G装甲吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.27,0:08:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乌拿加，木马拜托你去弄停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可大意呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，请出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和作战一样去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接近敌方后，我会布好圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要忘记打败钢弹就可取胜呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了，阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看他，阿姆罗！MS有点怪吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.51,0:08:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为米加粒子和岩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能分辨呢！         看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.02,0:08:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，瞄准吧！         我试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要快点分体      明白！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.19,0:09:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹，G战机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像被敌方布下了圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加尔，准备出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，配置准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.24,0:09:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙马鲁军曹，又再开始战斗吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人你只要去想回复健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是任务呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那虽也明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我的伤势没想像中严重呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.98,0:10:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再休息多一天，就可行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在忍耐吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有型的关口呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可说是病人的打扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要乱来呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有调节好的卫星，真荒废呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.36,0:10:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轰隆轰隆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加拿加，怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.50,0:10:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很顺利，拉拉有70%的准确率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去沙自巴鲁吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了畜牧和种植的德克撒斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因战争而实行不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有八个月以来，一直是荒废着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.95,0:10:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此变成了沙漠，也住不了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么？来了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了？是什么来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.03,0:10:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么？这是什么？有什么来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加拿加，是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是测试目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.41,0:11:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前为此没有这不明的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有和我一样的人在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，现在说了什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐在触摸我的内心感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.23,0:11:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我？拉拉，可否别说笑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.97,0:11:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么呢？现在那发麻的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是熟手的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是看清了方式呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹和G战机进入德克撒斯区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.79,0:11:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌方的舰队动向怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有变化，慢慢的移动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.39,0:11:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后的一台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是引诱我到那家伙那里的作战吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.44,0:12:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，来吧！钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.30,0:12:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙，狡猾...的想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终，终于...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.02,0:12:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因正派的去战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才会遇上这样的呀！钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃去德克撒斯吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在看什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.42,0:14:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐，不可以吗？      不介意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能操控爱美号吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在害怕吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只有去习惯吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我何时也在你的身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样，拉拉很快便成为比我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更好的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.61,0:14:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...比红色彗星更好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.44,0:14:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然吧！如不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不会收留拉拉你回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.38,0:14:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在卫星六号，使你有悲哀的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.65,0:14:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐，马克贝大佐用MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入了德克撒斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马克贝吗？真少有呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马克贝竟发生此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有用自己开发的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.41,0:14:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去打倒木马的想法，充满自信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有我在的吧，如不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.85,0:15:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不会做这么大意的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.02,0:15:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是也不能袖手旁观呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盖古克的装备完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因是Proto类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可说是完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.03,0:15:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样作为测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.33,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去看马克贝的样子吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.77,0:15:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敌舰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳‧波，令钢加农出发吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马加，敌舰是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.62,0:15:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知比一台，武沙二台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么？         明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.69,0:16:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盖古克的资料已重新装好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿普通的制服也可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.66,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就算坐上MS，也一定会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不想死的意志呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不会穿战斗的制服呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟有这细小炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，在安全的地方好好看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同样是MS战斗的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.32,0:17:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，给我看马克贝的本领吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.97,0:18:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三，二，一，请！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也藏在这旁的岩石中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能避吗？还是那新类型的本领？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是同伴的MS吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红色的MS！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亚吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.81,0:19:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚，走开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在的任务，不是去打击钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.12,0:19:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同伴在苦战，不可不管的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.46,0:19:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因我的战斗，才引到钢弹来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.93,0:19:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交给我吧！马克贝大佐，来了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.27,0:19:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来确定目前为此的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.41,0:19:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才用得太多雷射光了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.61,0:20:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能收拾钢弹，多谢的想，马克贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好的做呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，在看着吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.19,0:20:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐为何不去救他呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.23,0:20:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.17,0:20:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这个，刚才开始的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.17,0:21:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能驾驶这台的你，力量输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了不令夏亚成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不打败钢弹不行呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.49,0:21:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请停吧！已完了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乌拿加，把那壶送到去基西利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.08,0:21:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人那里吧！那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.35,0:21:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好东西呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.92,0:21:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个看到吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.46,0:21:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装模作样的能做到什么呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.10,0:21:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.32,0:22:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁？是谁在看着我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这...   不是夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.62,0:22:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿...姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.39,0:23:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉...拉！

